We’re excited to welcome our community to **Joy Club 华人长者“聚乐部”** on **April 18, 2026**! This special gathering marks **CCAKD’s first social event for Chinese seniors** in spring 2026 — a warm opportunity to meet new friends, reconnect with familiar faces, and enjoy time together in a friendly community setting.

If you or a loved one would enjoy a joyful afternoon of connection and companionship, we’d love to have you join us. Please help spread the word to seniors in our community and families who may be interested.

[Registration / Info](https://events.ccakd.ca/event/4/joy-club)
